ITDEV 117 Milestone Project 1

Movie Theater App

The app will allow the moviegoing audience looking to see a movie and order food. 
The app will allow users to create a log in, choose a movie to see, a specific time to see said movie, and pre-order multiple food items. Upon completion of choices a ticket price will total all chosen items, and display a finalized ticket to the user. The app will also be used by the theater to track the wants of the user.

The app will work like this:
Login 
Create
Existing user log-in
Selection then begins
Movie and time selection 
Movie with times and costs display
User makes choices
Displays selections and running total 
Food ordering 
Food options display
User makes choice with ability to add another item
Cost adds to running total, and displays choices
Checkout
Displays all user choices with totals.
